    /usr/man/man8/safe-crux.8.gz
    /usr/share/safe-crux/bin/*
    /usr/share/safe-crux/doc/*
    /usr/share/safe-crux/addons/*

    from the script we should try to read first the user config file
    which is an overlay for configuration variables:
    ~/.safe-crux.conf

    and also the first time we must to create all required directories:
    ~/.safe-crux/mnt
    ~/.safe-crux/iso
    ~/.safe-crux/img


  - example of installation with PREFIX=/usr

